    "Name": "Haruna HAR-111",
    "Details": "The HAR-111 is the export variant of the Haruna, stripping out all Clan technology while retaining the core design philosophy. Guardian ECM powers the Stealth armor, MASC still pushes the 35-ton frame past 170 kph and the Vibroblade remains as the primary close-range threat. A Medium X-Pulse Laser replaces the Heavy Medium Laser and twin Streak SRM 2s handle ranged harassment. This model reached the Magistracy of Canopus and Fronc Reaches markets.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
